Barked at a train. Felt powerful.
The first 2 entries are created by ChatGPT but they are too funny to delete lol
Just got message back from my healthcare provider, they are 'considering' granting me the laser hair removal...
OMG I JUST CODED SOMETHING BY MYSELF AND IT WORKED SUCK A COCK CHATGPT! I made it so the Blog and Pawprints tabs also play the bark sound!

Been thinking about the Succubus puppy girl lable... Its so weird to me how it just fits me. I feel like a fucking Isekai character 'the story how I got reincarnated as a trans puppy girl thats constantly horny'. Looking at the me from just half a year ago this is a completely diffrent person. I like how I turned out or rather how I am turning out but damn its just so diffrent. All I want to do is become a hot bitch that makes men at the beach jealous of my polycule. Taking estrogen is THE best thing that ever happened to me. <3

This story is absolutely amazing. I cant believe how much I relate to the main character. The paragraph about her chosen apperance is like copied right out of my brain.... I can not put into words what this story just did to me.

Gosh being a woman is the best thing ever, I love my emotions and what estrogen does to my body... My thoughts have changed so much since I started taking estrogen, its probably just me being more honest to myself and damn what a difference that makes. I truly feel connected to myself now. I just say what I really think nowadays instead of what I think people want to hear, feels much healthier. Living for myself instead of living for the fear of missing out is also a much diffrent experience. I just want to live like this! I want to be. Everything is so much brighter and more colourful than it ever was before. I still have some hurdles to get over, I NEED bottom surgery for example. I honestly dont think a life with a penis will be a life worth living for me, I can tolerate the thing because I still need it for the surgery but damn I hate it so much. To end on a high node Im going to spend the day with my gf talking and playing games online I am unimaginably happy rn. <3

Holy shit Im in love! She is so amazing, my girlfiend was over for the weekend and HOLY SHIT! I could cuddle with her forever and we did some other fun stuff too but damn. She just needed to brush the right spot with a finger and I melted into a horny, needy poudle of absolute pleasour
